Pakistan bought 6,000 tonnes of rbd palmoil at its import tender today for first half May shipment,traders said.    The price was believed to be in the region of 345.50 dlrsper tonne cost and freight, but confirmation is awaited, theysaid.    Pakistan sought to buy up to 12,000 tonnes for first halfMay and has not said when it is likely to tender for thebalance. REUTER&#3;